    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1899-08-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1899-08-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="450"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d450">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Governor <persName type="from">Foster</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">State of Louisiana, Executive Department</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Baton Rouge</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-08-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 3, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge receipt of your
                    favor confirming your telegram notifying me of the appointment by the Italian
                    Government of Marquis Romano to be acting consul.</p>
                <pb facs="0545" n="449" xml:id="pg_449"/>
                <p>I have already communicated with him as such, and requested him to fix a day
                    suitable to his pleasure to meet me in his official capacity.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Murphy J. Foster.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
